bounds = [(0.0, 1.0) for _ in range(3)]
linear_constraints = torch.tensor([[1, -1, 0]], dtype=torch.double
    ), torch.tensor([[0]], dtype=torch.double)
def test_rounding_func(x: Tensor) ->Tensor:
    return x
gen_sobol = _generate_sobol_points(n_sobol=100, bounds=bounds, device=torch
    .device('cpu'), linear_constraints=linear_constraints, rounding_func=
    test_rounding_func)
self.assertEqual(len(gen_sobol), 100)
self.assertIsInstance(gen_sobol, Tensor)
